<s> Are there any  </s>
<s> WAI recommendations about this?  </s>
<s> I have tried pages out that have search fields as well as login screens, and they seem to work quite well with screenreaders: the screenreader first reads the "label+edit" and then  </s>
<s> proceeds reading the rest of the page until a user starts entering their  </s>
